## Commit Note

Committed VAK_3b / VAkK_3.21.

Established:
- avidyā condenses prior afflictions
- saṃskārāḥ condense prior karma
- vijñāna is the junction-aggregate, not generic consciousness
- nāmarūpa follows as the first psycho-physical determination

Logical determination:
VAkK_3.21 begins filling the 2/8/2 architecture of VAkK_3.20. The prior limit is kleśa-karma compressed as avidyā-saṃskāra. The present middle begins at the junction as vijñāna, then unfolds as nāmarūpa.
